{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_8hCQNH9ylMlS8DpY1tLUHYN5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Review-Spec Stage Complete — TST-001\n\n### Status: **BLOCKED** — PRD Not Ready\n\nThe PRD review report (`aidd/reports/prd/TST-001.json`) shows `recommended_status=pending`. Implementation is blocked until these issues are resolved.\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Findings\n\n#### PRD Issues (Critical)\n| Finding | Severity | Description |\n|---------|----------|-------------|\n| Placeholders in PRD | Major | PRD contains template placeholders (`<этапы/флаги/откат>`, `<Описание проблемы>`, etc.) |\n| Format guidance markers | Major | Contains formatting instructions instead of actual answers |\n| Narrative/structured mismatch | Warn | PRD structure doesn't match expected format |\n\n#### PRD Review Subagent Findings\n| ID | Finding | Severity |\n|----|---------|----------|\n| F1 | Authentication model mismatch — PRD assumes JWT, codebase uses header-based (X-Profile-Key) | CRITICAL |\n| F2 | State management mismatch — PRD assumes Redux, codebase uses Zustand | CRITICAL |\n| F3 | WebSocket vs SSE gap — PRD requires WebSocket, but SSE infrastructure exists | HIGH |\n| F4 | Missing Spring Security dependency | HIGH |\n| F5 | No audit_log table schema defined | MEDIUM |\n| F6 | Incomplete roll-out section | LOW |\n\n#### Plan Review Subagent Findings (APPROVED with WARN)\n| ID | Finding | Severity |\n|----|---------|----------|\n| R-007 | Component scan may miss RBAC beans — need RbacConfig in all profiles | MEDIUM |\n| R-008 | Profile service integration undefined — no backend API for fetching roles | HIGH |\n\n---\n\n### Required Next Action\n\n**Run the spec-interview to resolve open questions and fix PRD placeholders:**\n\n```\n/feature-dev-aidd:spec-interview TST-001\n```\n\nThis will:\n1. Address the authentication model mismatch (JWT vs headers)\n2. Clarify state management approach (Redux vs Zustand)\n3. Resolve SSE vs WebSocket decision\n4. Fill in placeholder sections in the PRD\n5. Define audit_log schema requirements\n\n---\n\n### Report Artifacts\n- PRD review report: `aidd/reports/prd/TST-001.json`\n- Plan review: Completed (approved with WARN conditions)\n- PRD review: Completed (status: NEEDS_REVISION)"}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":25645,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":25645,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"386f7333-beca-450a-9559-9ee7ee33b01e","uuid":"539aa023-a2d6-4997-b482-13f24c8c1c1d"}
